      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KRIS BAR IMOGEN (4) goes very well at the course and distance with two wins and a placing from four starts. Recorded a 7 length win (23.96) in a Bottom Up - Restricted Win last time at this track. Looks the one to beat with even luck. COLLINDA RAMSAY (3) showed good early speed and led throughout to score his maiden two back then finished second last start and beaten 5 lengths at this track over 425m (24.39). Has placed two times at this trip. Can feature again this time. THOUGHT OF THAT (7) is long overdue for a win, finishing in the minors at his last three starts, the latest jumping from this same box when third in a T3 Grade 6 at this track (24.45). Rates a leading chance. HARTLAND BONNIE (1) was out of the money here last time out but can bounce back.",
